I will now proceed with scaffolding the Fastify API server as per the instructions. This involves adding necessary dependencies, creating a structured server with plugins for database connectivity and routes for a health check, and setting up the main application entry point to run the server.

First, I will update `apps/api/package.json` to include the required dependencies for Fastify, CORS, environment variables, and development logging.

